	1. i will check server logs to identify the reason for application down. it shows db connectivity error if db is down.
	2. normally we have db cluster. if db instance is down, i will try to make it up. if it doesnt, i will ask the team to change the configuration to connect to other instance of the cluster.
	3. mean while will create RCA and assign to db team
